            "failure_message": "Wrath-driven eruption only: requires very high wrath with high arousal and negative valence. Blocks cold/contained hostility by capping smoldering_anger and requiring wrath to dominate it. Enforces restraint-loss via low (or sharply dropping) inhibitory_control, with trait self_control making eruption harder unless disinhibition is stronger. Prosocial/harm-aware tones remain capped, and a recent spike/jump is required so it reads as a post-snap blowout rather than baseline heat."
